data.description: Almost brand new home for sale in Riverdale Schools! This home sits at the dead end of a quiet street.  The home boasts a fantastic layout with an open concept living/kitchen area.  The kitchen offers ample cabinetry and a huge butcher block island.  It even has a small nook where you can set up an office.  The master bedroom sits on one side of the house with the other bedrooms on the opposite side.  All of the bedrooms are a nice size.  The home sits on almost a half acre of property so there's plenty of space to play.  This is a great home for anyone looking.  Come take a look!
